Clément Duhour https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cl%C3%A9ment_Duhour 0 Clément Duhour was born in Saint-Jean d’Anglet, in the Aquitaine region of south-western France on 11 December 1912. He died on 3 January 1983 in Neuilly-sur-Seine. He was a French athlete, singer, actor, film director and producer.
